Title: Fischer metal cavity fixing 5 x 37mm (20)
Description: Versatile fixings with metric screws, these Fischer HM-S cavity metal anchors are suitable for all panel building materials, fixing lights, towel rails and curtain rails. Set with Fischer installation pliers HM-Z 1 in pre-positioned installation, these fixings are pulled into the cavity against the board building material with pliers, expanding arms swinging open to press onto the reverse side of the board. As an alternative, assembly can be carried out with a screwdriver.
category: Trade Essentials/Fixings and Fasteners/Fixings/Cavity Fixings/Cavity Fixings.csv -> Fischer metal cavity fixing 5 x 37mm (20)

Title: Fischer DuoTec 537260 nylon toggle cavity fix 10mm (20)
Description: Suitable for use on high tensile and transverse loads, the Fischer DuoTec 10mm nylon toggle cavity fix and panhead screw is strong enough for radiator and TV bracket fixing. Easy to use, even in narrow or insulated cavities, these plugs and screws offer small 10mm drill hole diameters and a short toggle element. With no cutting required for easier, safer fitting into gypsum, DuoTec plugs won't fall into the drill hole, even without a screw, making pre-install straightforward. Automatically folding behind the panel for added strength, the plug's toggle element works alongside a flexible stainless steel screw seat for reliable use with wood and chipboard screws or metric hooks and threaded rods with lock nuts.

Title: Fischer DuoLine DuoBlade selfdrilling plasterboard plug and screw (25)
Description: Featuring different components chosen for their high levels of performance, these Fischer DuoLine DuoBlade self-drilling plasterboard plugs and screws is part of the reliable DuoLine range. With a self-drilling tip, DuoBlade allows for effective drilling when a fixing is screwed into the installation pre-position with screwdriver setting tool flush to the surface of gypsum plasterboard. Universally suitable for fixing, this plug and screw system offers excellent performance with 4 - 5mm wood, metal and chipboard screws and hook and eye screws, making it suitable for a variety of fitting jobs, ranging from smoke detectors to curtain rods and shutters. Compatible with a conventional PZ2 drive, DuoBlade doesn't need a special setting device.
